{"tid":1912040,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)生死時速","createTime":"2020-03-05T18:54:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T21:21:19.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e24b79b575c198c8ff2a70706c81db229e391aa7","tid":1912040,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T18:54:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=e707ba46\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=7138f7df\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=1c03ec42\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/c5/Speedposter.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fc5%2FSpeedposter.jpg&h=5581070f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下班時間，在洛杉磯一棟大樓的上班族，準備搭乘電梯回家，卻不知大樓電梯已被一名炸彈客裝置炸彈，炸彈客打算利用困在電梯的人質達成目的，但是洛杉磯警察局特殊武器戰術小組警員傑克&middot;崔文（Cst. Jack Traven，基努&middot;李維飾演）發揮智慧與勇氣，破壞了炸彈客的計畫，成功救出了人質。崔文試圖進一步逮住炸彈客，但炸彈客終究還是逃之夭夭<br />\n<br />\n4 15AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=02d6f74a\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=b4ef8df7\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d1667342b72b840ade336614c77201c11c6e386","tid":1912040,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T18:55:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15f8dd80992c81f1f4390cf7fce23be16c1d558","tid":1912040,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T19:52:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c756b32fb6bdeb1a329fe569816b5a658fb82a0b","tid":1912040,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T20:33:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hk